{"prompt": "Generate a website for a sustainable fashion brand. The website should be futuristic and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Aura Wear</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-blue: #0a4ef0;\n            --secondary-blue: #578aff;\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #0d0d0d;\n        }\n\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--brand-blue), var(--secondary-blue));\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(10, 78, 240, 0.3);\n            position: sticky;\n            top: 0;\n            z-index: 1000;\n        }\n\n        header .container {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .logo {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            display: flex;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            margin-left: 30px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: 500;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease, text-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-blue);\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(87, 138, 255, 0.7);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            height: 80vh;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(10, 78, 240, 0.8), rgba(13, 13, 13, 0.9)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x800/0a4ef0/ffffff?text=AURA+WEAR+FUTURE') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(10, 78, 240, 0.1) 50%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7) 90%);\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2;\n            max-width: 800px;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 4em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(87, 138, 255, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: var(--brand-blue);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            border-radius: 30px;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid transparent;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(10, 78, 240, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background: var(--secondary-blue);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(87, 138, 255, 0.7);\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n            border-color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 60px;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(10, 78, 240, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border: 1px solid rgba(10, 78, 240, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(10, 78, 240, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(10, 78, 240, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--secondary-blue);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        .gallery {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item img:hover {\n            transform: scale(1.05);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(87, 138, 255, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background: var(--brand-blue);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n            box-shadow: 0 -4px 15px rgba(10, 78, 240, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .logo {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            nav ul {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                text-align: center;\n                margin-top: 20px;\n            }\n            nav ul li {\n                margin: 10px 0;\n            }\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 3em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            section h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 480px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1em;\n            }\n            .cta-button {\n                font-size: 1em;\n                padding: 12px 25px;\n            }\n            .feature-grid, .gallery {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"logo\">Aura Wear</div>\n            <nav>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><a href=\"#about\">About</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#features\">Features</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#gallery\">Gallery</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n                </ul>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h1>Future of Sustainable Fashion</h1>\n            <p>Innovating style with eco-conscious materials and futuristic design.</p>\n            <a href=\"#gallery\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Collections</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Our Vision</h2>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 1.2em;\">\n            Aura Wear is at the forefront of a new era in fashion, where style meets sustainability. We harness advanced material science and ethical production to create garments that are not only aesthetically striking but also gentle on our planet. Our mission is to redefine luxury by making conscious consumption the ultimate statement.\n        </p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"features\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Core Principles</h2>\n            <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-leaf\"></i>\n                    <h3>Eco-Conscious Materials</h3>\n                    <p>Utilizing recycled, organic, and biodegradable fabrics.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-recycle\"></i>\n                    <h3>Circular Design</h3>\n                    <p>Products designed for longevity and recyclability.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\"></i>\n                    <h3>Innovative Technology</h3>\n                    <p>Leveraging bio-fabrication and smart textile solutions.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-users\"></i>\n                    <h3>Ethical Production</h3>\n                    <p>Fair labor practices and transparent supply chains.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"gallery\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Gallery</h2>\n            <div class=\"gallery\">\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\"><img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x400/0a4ef0/ffffff?text=Collection+A\" alt=\"Aura Wear Collection A\"></div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\"><img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x400/578aff/ffffff?text=Collection+B\" alt=\"Aura Wear Collection B\"></div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\"><img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x400/0a4ef0/ffffff?text=Collection+C\" alt=\"Aura Wear Collection C\"></div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\"><img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x400/578aff/ffffff?text=Collection+D\" alt=\"Aura Wear Collection D\"></div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Connect with Us</h2>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n            Discover the future of fashion. Follow us on our journey to a more sustainable world.\n        </p>\n        <div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n            <a href=\"mailto:info@aurawear.com\" class=\"cta-button\" style=\"background: var(--secondary-blue);\">Get in Touch</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2077 Aura Wear. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Innovating fashion for a brighter future.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple scroll animation for navigation links\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}